Class ElevatedAbstractReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.fluent.AbstractReference
      • net.dean.jraw.fluent.ElevatedAbstractReference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Reference
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlairReference, InboxReference, UserReference

    public class ElevatedAbstractReference
extends AbstractReference
    This class provides a constructor that requires a ManagerAggregation instead of a RedditClient, like what AbstractReference does. This aggregation is visible to subclasses through the managers field.
